                           </div>
                        </td>
                        <td valign="bottom" width="80"></td>
                     </tr>
                     <tr>
                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24">2.</td>
                        <td colspan="5" valign="top" width="288">Any augmentation shall occur no sooner than 30 days after notification in writing to the chairpersons of the committees and
