                        <td valign="top" width="24">11.</td>
                        <td colspan="5" valign="top" width="288">
                           <div style="">Of the amounts appropriated in Schedule (1), $325,000 shall be allocated by the Judicial Council in order to reimburse the
                              California State Auditor for the costs of trial court audits incurred by the California State Auditor pursuant to Section
                              19210 of the Public Contract Code.
                           </div>
                        </td>
