                           facing, statewide development and implementation of Next Generation 9-1-1. Such challenges include technological, operational,
                           and legal or contractual challenges, as well as other challenges identified by the Office. The reports shall also include
                           information on proposed solutions to these identified challenges, the potential costs of such solutions, effects on and changes
