                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24">4.</td>
                        <td colspan="5" valign="top" width="288">
                           <div style="">Of the amount appropriated in Schedule (3), $3,000,000 shall be used to add capacity in the Consumer Protection Section focused
                              on tenant protection and enforcing the rights of tenants. This finding shall supplement and not supplant existing department
                              work in this area, and may not be directed to other section work.
                           </div>
                        </td>
                        <td valign="bottom" width="80"></td>
                     </tr>
