                     <tr>
                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24">2.</td>
                        <td colspan="5" valign="top" width="288">
                           <div style="">Notwithstanding any other law, the Director of Finance may authorize a loan from the General Fund, in an amount not to exceed
                              45 percent of reimbursements appropriated in Schedule (9) of this item, to the Department of Forestry and Fire Protection,
                              provided that:
                           </div>
                        </td>
                        <td valign="bottom" width="80"></td>
