                        <td valign="top" width="24">24.</td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24">(a)</td>
                        <td colspan="4" valign="top" width="264">Of the amounts appropriated in Schedule (2), $15,000,000 shall be made available for Title X family planning funding to maintain
                           and support the delivery of equitable, affordable, high quality, client-centered family planning services to eligible patients
                           with low-incomes across the state.
