                        <td valign="top" width="24">(b)</td>
                        <td colspan="4" valign="top" width="264">The State Department of Health Care Services shall receive and provide the funds to Essential Access Health, the designated
                           statewide federal Title X grantee, no later than September 30, 2025. 
                        </td>
                        <td align="right" valign="bottom" width="80"></td>
                     </tr>
