                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24">(c)</td>
                        <td colspan="4" valign="top" width="264">Funding provided to Essential Access Health may be used for the following purposes:</td>
                        <td align="right" valign="bottom" width="80"></td>
                     </tr>
                     <tr>
                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
