                     <tr>
                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24">28.</td>
                        <td colspan="5" valign="top" width="288">
                           <div style="">Of the funds appropriated in this item, $77,000 is provided to support 0.5 existing position to update existing, and develop
                              new, resources and strategies, and in-service teacher training to support lesbian, gay, bisexual, transgender, queer, and
                              questioning students, pursuant to Chapter 775 of the Statutes of 2019.
