                     </tr>
                     <tr>
                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24">17.</td>
                        <td colspan="5" valign="top" width="288">Of the funds appropriated in Schedule (1), $422,000 and 2.0 positions are available to support legal staffing needs in the
