                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24">2.3.</td>
                        <td colspan="5" valign="top" width="288">
                           <div style="">Of the funds appropriated in this item, $35,000,000 is provided on an ongoing basis to support the Graduation Initiative 2025.
                              This funding shall be used exclusively to support efforts to close equity gaps in graduation rates for low-income students
                              and historically underrepresented students. California
